New Records: Highest-ever T20 international first powerplay score of 113/1 for the opening six overs
Key Match Events: Mitchell Marsh smashed 30 off one over from Jack Jarvis
Both Head and Marsh fell to Mark Watt in the seventh over but the damage was already done
Josh Inglis picked up the baton with a quick-fire unbeaten 27
Miscellaneous Highlights: Jake Fraser-McGurk fell to a three-ball duck
Sean Abbott was the pick of the Australia bowlers with three for 39
